{"tid":1355098,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[歷史研究] 戰鬥民族教你用雨遮 丫唔係 係刺刀！","createTime":"2019-07-23T09:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T01:42:17.000Z","uid":275921,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5c3f1105db8d5a432c0218c89c94cbbb3bf98f","tid":1355098,"uid":275921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"開始之前，提醒返大家，以下既內容係學術討論，<br />\n方便大家整戰棋公仔或者係理解刺刀術發展脈絡，<br />\n請唔好亂咁試呀，好危險架嘛，拮親人點算呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起二次大戰既戰鬥民族，大家可能淨係諗起一堆拎住衝鋒槍既痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但由於生產問題同埋戰術需要<br />\n所以好多蘇軍都仲係拎栓式步槍／半自動步槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以由正規步兵到遊擊隊，都好重視一樣野，就係刺刀訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄軍既刺刀術，源自於19世紀法國陸軍既Bayonet Fencing（姑且譯做刺刀劍術）<br />\n而大家又可以想像，係一場總體戰入面，好難有時間慢慢訓練<br />\n所以刺刀訓練都盡可能地簡化，以下既解說就係1942年派俾遊擊隊既教範<br />\n唔好以為係俾遊擊隊就好hea，因為蘇軍遊擊隊係42年開始由蘇軍最高統帥部指揮<br />\n唔止係敵後騷擾，仲會炸鐵路炸火車，以及配合正規軍行動<br />\n佢地收到既刺刀訓練手冊，同正規軍基本上係一樣，不過簡化左方便學<br />\n<br />\n如上所述，俄軍刺刀術源自法軍，所以佢既企法，<span style=\"color: red;\">同西洋劍一樣係丁字步</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果係右手持槍的話，就係左腳前指，右腳係後方成90度直角</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/bajonet1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Fbajonet1.jpg&h=1f2f2c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">右手持步槍扳機位置（即係大概遮既手把位），左手持槍身中段位置</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j761VAH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj761VAH.png&h=99a83d28&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n如果想向前移動，好自然咁前腳先踏前，後腳跟上一步<br />\n後退的話，重心移向前腳，後腳先退，然後前腳後退一步<br />\n或者好似成日睇劍擊比賽見到咁，依個上youtube參考下會比文字描述清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攻擊方法黎講，主要可以分成兩種：<span style=\"color: red;\">刺擊，棍棒攻擊（Clubbing）</span><br />\n而刺擊又可以分成兩種，分別係：<br />\n先格擋／撥開對方攻擊後 趁對方中門大開既<span style=\"color: red;\">快速刺擊（Jab thrust）</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idNsQ9z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidNsQ9z.png&h=93a43adc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以及<span style=\"color: red;\">弓步擊（Lunge），弓步擊仲可以細分為低弓步擊同高弓步擊</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYS1ba0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYS1ba0.png&h=f5953ced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩者都係右腳大步踏前發動攻擊，<br />\n分別係前者槍端微向上刺擊，後者肩膀高度水平刺擊<br />\n棍擊方面，就比較簡單，就係雙手持槍端，舉高過頭向下揮擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n必要時可以同弓步擊一樣，右腳踏前加打揮擊力度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pUDopxf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpUDopxf.png&h=8d1628f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然啦，如果對面既法西斯中門大開，43年開始紅軍仲會教士兵<span style=\"color: red;\">踢春袋</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者係右邊咁樣，一掌下而上打佢下巴（個人覺得用槍托仲實際）<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/russtrn10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Frusstrn10.jpg&h=c06c3096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n講完攻擊就到防守啦，防守方面，<br />\n面對敵人由上而下既攻擊，不論係棍同劍都好，都係用一個叫<span style=\"color: red;\">High Parry</span>既動作起手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6KFewdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6KFewdt.png&h=e2ae6485&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n然後有兩個反擊方法，其一係右腳踏前，順勢將對方劈擊偏斜開，<span style=\"color: red;\">然後一個槍托掃過去</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kv0uj7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkv0uj7g.png&h=3c30f3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其二就係相反，擋完將對方攻擊偏斜/撥向持槍手方向<br />\n再用返上面提過既快速刺擊（Jab thrust）<br />\n<br />\n假如對方同樣用刺擊類武器，咁防守方法主要都係先招架，後反擊<br />\n招架方法同樣都分兩種，分別係撥左撥右，然後接快速刺擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qptvO2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqptvO2a.png&h=a75ba416&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n或者係招架完後向上或者向下壓，再視情況接快速刺擊或者弓步擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CwHMnnq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCwHMnnq.png&h=c2ba7e2d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另一方面，如果對方用刀劍／棍類武器，<br />\n但唔係拉晒弓上而下揮擊，而係左右水平揮擊既話，都有兩個處理方法<br />\n其一係用返以上招架技巧（參考返上幾行），其二係用以下既招架方法<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/pombay1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Fpombay1.gif&h=5af46d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依種招架方法常見於17-19世紀早期 由長槍類武器演化既刺槍術 但刺劍術並唔常見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">簡單總結一下，戰鬥民族二戰既刺槍術有以下幾個特點：<br />\n1. 攻擊以刺擊同槍托棒擊為主<br />\n2. 防守方面，以步槍撥開／格擋對方攻擊，然後進行反擊<br />\n3. 基本上無任何刺刀斬擊動作，因為刺刀只可以刺，揮擊係無能架</span><br />\n<br />\n到最後，順便講埋19世紀刺刀係點隊形作戰啦<br />\n由於當時仲係採用線式陣列，視唔同國家既作戰教條，列成兩／三行排槍射擊<br />\n所以防守對方衝鋒時，最基本陣形都係咁（英軍）<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/pombay2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Fpombay2.gif&h=d47b6a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者係排成三行或更多（法軍）<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/pintop14.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Fpintop14.gif&h=c89f6382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果係面對騎兵衝鋒／被包圍，就會採用大家都好熟既方陣<br />\n有趣既係，法軍1837年刺刀手冊入面，防守陣形仲有分成四個人<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/pinlow7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Fpinlow7.gif&h=cf9da905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者係好多好多人，咁就真係成個方陣咁啦<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/pinlow8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Fpinlow8.gif&h=16bdbba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家一齊學術討論，但係記得唔好亂試呀，真係好危險架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704bfb894df45ee1731af05524e4b5ed2e990a6a","tid":1355098,"uid":245784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7b99ef0c51132dfc785d8f9136ba377725f8eb","tid":1355098,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83838a4628ed3dca1b3d64dbfc22727751a68088","tid":1355098,"uid":145496,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:20:22.000Z","msg":"學撥同刺就夠<br />\n<br />\n雨遮太軟，其他動作做唔到"},{"pid":"ac120b244c6d026130c2438ef794d7ba341c0de4","tid":1355098,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:28:49.000Z","msg":"刺刀吉人一刀就ko到<br />\n遮吉唔死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當棍用可能實用啲"},{"pid":"8bf3c90f213a09281ae71cedbce78a43dda5e95c","tid":1355098,"uid":1297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:52:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fd8e0d8fa12609ef6b0eb06468c7fc83a8f4cf1f","tid":1355098,"uid":162854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5daf129708a2d7a628a9773d1e62cd9c7f7c49","tid":1355098,"uid":275921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b5c3f1105db8d5a432c0218c89c94cbbb3bf98f","tid":1355098,"uid":275921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"開始之前，提醒返大家，以下既內容係學術討論，<br />\n方便大家整戰棋公仔或者係理解刺刀術發展脈絡，<br />\n請唔好亂咁試呀，好危險架嘛，拮親人點算呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起二次大戰既戰鬥民族，大家可能淨係諗起一堆拎住衝鋒槍既痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但由於生產問題同埋戰術需要<br />\n所以好多蘇軍都仲係拎栓式步槍／半自動步槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以由正規步兵到遊擊隊，都好重視一樣野，就係刺刀訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄軍既刺刀術，源自於19世紀法國陸軍既Bayonet Fencing（姑且譯做刺刀劍術）<br />\n而大家又可以想像，係一場總體戰入面，好難有時間慢慢訓練<br />\n所以刺刀訓練都盡可能地簡化，以下既解說就係1942年派俾遊擊隊既教範<br />\n唔好以為係俾遊擊隊就好hea，因為蘇軍遊擊隊係42年開始由蘇軍最高統帥部指揮<br />\n唔止係敵後騷擾，仲會炸鐵路炸火車，以及配合正規軍行動<br />\n佢地收到既刺刀訓練手冊，同正規軍基本上係一樣，不過簡化左方便學<br />\n<br />\n如上所述，俄軍刺刀術源自法軍，所以佢既企法，<span style=\"color: red;\">同西洋劍一樣係丁字步</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果係右手持槍的話，就係左腳前指，右腳係後方成90度直角</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/bajonet1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Fbajonet1.jpg&h=1f2f2c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">右手持步槍扳機位置（即係大概遮既手把位），左手持槍身中段位置</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j761VAH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj761VAH.png&h=99a83d28&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n如果想向前移動，好自然咁前腳先踏前，後腳跟上一步<br />\n後退的話，重心移向前腳，後腳先退，然後前腳後退一步<br />\n或者好似成日睇劍擊比賽見到咁，依個上youtube參考下會比文字描述清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攻擊方法黎講，主要可以分成兩種：<span style=\"color: red;\">刺擊，棍棒攻擊（Clubbing）</span><br />\n而刺擊又可以分成兩種，分別係：<br />\n先格擋／撥開對方攻擊後 趁對方中門大開既<span style=\"color: red;\">快速刺擊（Jab thrust）</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idNsQ9z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidNsQ9z.png&h=93a43adc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以及<span style=\"color: red;\">弓步擊（Lunge），弓步擊仲可以細分為低弓步擊同高弓步擊</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYS1ba0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYS1ba0.png&h=f5953ced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩者都係右腳大步踏前發動攻擊，<br />\n分別係前者槍端微向上刺擊，後者肩膀高度水平刺擊<br />\n棍擊方面，就比較簡單，就係雙手持槍端，舉高過頭向下揮擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n必要時可以同弓步擊一樣，右腳踏前加打揮擊力度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pUDopxf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpUDopxf.png&h=8d1628f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然啦，如果對面既法西斯中門大開，43年開始紅軍仲會教士兵<span style=\"color: red;\">踢春袋</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者係右邊咁樣，一掌下而上打佢下巴（個人覺得用槍托仲實際）<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/russtrn10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Frusstrn10.jpg&h=c06c3096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n講完攻擊就到防守啦，防守方面，<br />\n面對敵人由上而下既攻擊，不論係棍同劍都好，都係用一個叫<span style=\"color: red;\">High Parry</span>既動作起手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6KFewdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6KFewdt.png&h=e2ae6485&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n然後有兩個反擊方法，其一係右腳踏前，順勢將對方劈擊偏斜開，<span style=\"color: red;\">然後一個槍托掃過去</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kv0uj7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkv0uj7g.png&h=3c30f3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其二就係相反，擋完將對方攻擊偏斜/撥向持槍手方向<br />\n再用返上面提過既快速刺擊（Jab thrust）<br />\n<br />\n假如對方同樣用刺擊類武器，咁防守方法主要都係先招架，後反擊<br />\n招架方法同樣都分兩種，分別係撥左撥右，然後接快速刺擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qptvO2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqptvO2a.png&h=a75ba416&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n或者係招架完後向上或者向下壓，再視情況接快速刺擊或者弓步擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CwHMnnq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCwHMnnq.png&h=c2ba7e2d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另一方面，如果對方用刀劍／棍類武器，<br />\n但唔係拉晒弓上而下揮擊，而係左右水平揮擊既話，都有兩個處理方法<br />\n其一係用返以上招架技巧（參考返上幾行），其二係用以下既招架方法<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/pombay1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Fpombay1.gif&h=5af46d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依種招架方法常見於17-19世紀早期 由長槍類武器演化既刺槍術 但刺劍術並唔常見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">簡單總結一下，戰鬥民族二戰既刺槍術有以下幾個特點：<br />\n1. 攻擊以刺擊同槍托棒擊為主<br />\n2. 防守方面，以步槍撥開／格擋對方攻擊，然後進行反擊<br />\n3. 基本上無任何刺刀斬擊動作，因為刺刀只可以刺，揮擊係無能架</span><br />\n<br />\n到最後，順便講埋19世紀刺刀係點隊形作戰啦<br />\n由於當時仲係採用線式陣列，視唔同國家既作戰教條，列成兩／三行排槍射擊<br />\n所以防守對方衝鋒時，最基本陣形都係咁（英軍）<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/pombay2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Fpombay2.gif&h=d47b6a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者係排成三行或更多（法軍）<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/pintop14.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Fpintop14.gif&h=c89f6382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果係面對騎兵衝鋒／被包圍，就會採用大家都好熟既方陣<br />\n有趣既係，法軍1837年刺刀手冊入面，防守陣形仲有分成四個人<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/pinlow7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Fpinlow7.gif&h=cf9da905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者係好多好多人，咁就真係成個方陣咁啦<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thortrains.com/getright/pinlow8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thortrains.com%2Fgetright%2Fpinlow8.gif&h=16bdbba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家一齊學術討論，但係記得唔好亂試呀，真係好危險架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:12:19.000Z","msg":"原來lunge張圖up錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家補返張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vufx5DL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvufx5DL.png&h=6d4d3d29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1adddc1c7c4483f76ccd6d7a8ef9f3bc682eb6ad","tid":1355098,"uid":275921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac120b244c6d026130c2438ef794d7ba341c0de4","tid":1355098,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:28:49.000Z","msg":"刺刀吉人一刀就ko到<br />\n遮吉唔死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當棍用可能實用啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:24:30.000Z","msg":"撥開攻擊之後 再攞遮柄毆落去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過把遮唔夠重唔夠mass 當棍用都係唔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前既步槍可以用槍托打人 <br />\n都係因為果個位成大大舊實心木<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似樓上講咁 有咩危急關頭<br />\n可能識得撥同刺已經好好 起碼嚇得下人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f129a41fe147dc45c94326b00ed98b3cfaccae9","tid":1355098,"uid":155005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:27:02.000Z","msg":"中學比老母逼去軍校學過 希望用得翻"},{"pid":"f9f5e707db260d2edb97534baee1250f6e344337","tid":1355098,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:29:09.000Z","msg":"真。雨傘革命正式展開<br />\n平時去集會<br />\n或者呢排落去幫手做守衛隊既<br />\n可以用d空閒時間黎練練招<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163059b1537afd86991289c88bae20f7667bc0c1","tid":1355098,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac120b244c6d026130c2438ef794d7ba341c0de4","tid":1355098,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:28:49.000Z","msg":"刺刀吉人一刀就ko到<br />\n遮吉唔死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當棍用可能實用啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:33:27.000Z","msg":"三分木板穿透"},{"pid":"49a91b95a8ba199e9a4fd5d19d72e12c389ba9f3","tid":1355098,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:34:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n727和理非<br />\n元朗游行裝備<br />\n簡單方便全合法<br />\n帶頭盔<br />\n表達黑社會恐擊<br />\n帶木掃把<br />\n表達掃走黑社會<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"665ab6d11532f4a3e28addbb77bfd8585cd1d6fa","tid":1355098,"uid":125911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:40:03.000Z","msg":"好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThanks 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1459006d0fbb59e7d16e53790ad08994f33dfbb1","tid":1355098,"uid":275921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:31:29.000Z","msg":"啱啱見到依段1885年英軍刺刀訓練既解說影片<br />\n由於英軍既刺刀訓練，同樣係源自法國刺劍術<br />\n所以如果咁多位巴打睇完戰鬥民族既刺刀教範解說之後<br />\n想對於步法或者係動作仲有興趣 都歡迎望一望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JYQTFT9WU_I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJYQTFT9WU_I&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWIvgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=1ae684d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JYQTFT9WU_I</a><br />\n<br />\n段片入面其實有幾點值得注意：<br />\n1. 步法　<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前進係左腳先踏前，右腳隨後跟上一小步，後退相反</span><br />\n2. 動作　　<br />\n段片入面有幾個動作，係樓上蘇軍刺刀術係無既<br />\n包括low Guard (段片6:57), High Guard (8:03), Head Parry (8:51)<br />\n仲有就係Shortern Arms (9:26)<br />\n咁係因為Low Guard係用黎攻擊壕溝內既敵人<br />\nHigh Guard 係用黎攻擊企係高位既敵人<br />\nHead Parry主要係擋騎兵軍刀攻擊<br />\n至於Shortern Arms黎講，主要係因為19世紀末既步槍仲係好長<br />\n所以係用黎應付埋身肉搏既敵人<br />\n到1942/43年，基本上依四個動作已經無咁常用而省略左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.攻擊方法<br />\n基本上源自刺劍術既刺刀術，攻擊方法都係以拮為主<br />\n因為刺劍術由西洋劍擊演化出黎，細心留意會發現<br />\n其實Point/Thrust同埋Lunge，都係西洋劍既攻擊手法<br />\n只係刺刀術化短為長，化劍為槍，化單手為雙手<br />\n睇落已經係兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 防守方法<br />\n段片最後有少少鏡頭，大原則都係<span style=\"color: red;\">先撥開後反擊</span><br />\n記住呀，如非必要，特別係你把野唔夠硬淨<br />\n千祈唔好硬碰硬，借力打力撥開佢就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果想睇下我介紹既戰鬥民族刺刀術 實際用法係咩情況<br />\n可以睇下依段Bayonet Fencing既片<br />\n好多攻擊手法都係同教範十分類似，可以慢慢參詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UClIpGnV7c0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUClIpGnV7c0&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWIvgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=a1443cfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UClIpGnV7c0</a><br />\n<br />\n最後提多句，學術討論，唔好亂試呀，拮親人好危險架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79695eb898ffef51d920246a37737e0e5df488a","tid":1355098,"uid":275921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:42:17.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}